---
import ConvergentLayout from "../../layouts/convergentLayout.astro";
import globeMap from "../../images/globeMap.svg?raw";
---

<ConvergentLayout title="Public Square TO">
  <section
    aria-labelledby="hero-banner-title"
    class="hero-banner flex items-center flex-col gap-6 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16"
  >
    <h1 class="text-gray-500 flex flex-col" id="hero-banner-title">
      Public Square TO
      <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-black">
        Helping communities find common ground
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="max-w-2xl">
      Public Square TO helps make your voice heard on issues that affect your
      community. Your Voice Matters in Shaping Toronto
    </p>
    <a
      href="/"
      class="text-white bg-gray-500 p-2 rounded-xl w-min whitespace-nowrap"
      >View Demo Video</a
    >
  </section>
  <article
    id="info-1"
    class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-left max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16"
  >
    <h2 class="flex flex-col">
      What we have done
      <span class="text-3xl font-bold">
        Empowering Local Voices Through Polis
      </span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div id="info-1-img-placeholder" class="bg-amber-400 h-48"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center-safe">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Boost Engagement</h3>
        <p>Turn any community event into an interactive experience.</p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Real-Time Feedback</h3>
        <p>Capture meaningful input from attendees instantly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div id="info-1-img-placeholder" class="bg-amber-400 h-48 order-2"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center-safe order-1">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Simple Access</h3>
        <p>All you need is a smartphone, browser, and internet</p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Empower Communities</h3>
        <p>Give every voice a chance to be heard in public forums</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center py-16 bg-gray-200">
    <h2 class="flex flex-col max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      Our technology platform Polis
      <span class="text-3xl font-bold">
        Steps for Using Polis for Democratic Participation:
      </span>
    </h2>
    <div id="steps-grid" class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 px-8">
      <hgroup>
        <div class="img-placeholder text-3xl">‚ö°</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Choose Pol.is as Your Tool</h3>
        <p>
          Select Pol.is, a free and open-source platform, to support democratic
          participation.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup>
        <div class="img-placeholder text-3xl">‚õ≥</div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">
          Leverage AI-Powered Consensus Building
        </h3>
        <p>
          Utilize Pol.is‚Äôs AI capabilities to identify areas of consensus and
          disagreement among participants.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup>
        <div class="img-placeholder text-3xl">ü´Ç</div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Engage Participants Globally</h3>
        <p>
          Open the platform to a diverse audience to encourage wide civic
          engagement, regardless of location.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup>
        <div class="img-placeholder text-3xl">üìà</div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Analyze Input and Generate Insights</h3>
        <p>
          Let Pol.is process participants' input and visualize group opinions in
          real time, helping uncover shared views.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup>
        <div class="img-placeholder text-3xl">‚ù§Ô∏è</div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Adopt Best Practices from Global Use</h3>
        <p>
          Benefit from methods and strategies proven by local governments, civic
          groups, and major technology companies around the world.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup>
        <div class="img-placeholder text-3xl">üòä</div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Apply the Insights to Decision-Making</h3>
        <p>
          Use the consensus generated to guide policies, product decisions, or
          organizational strategies.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center py-16">
    <h2 class="flex flex-col">
      Success Stories
      <span class="text-3xl font-bold"> Global Use </span>
    </h2>
    <p>
      Discover how Pol.is is being used around the world to foster meaningful
      public dialogue and informed decision-making
    </p>
    <div id="world-map-container" class="max-w-full">
      <Fragment class="w-full" set:html={globeMap} />
    </div>
    <div id="steps-grid" class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 px-8">
      <hgroup class="h-full grid grid-rows-[3lh_1fr_min-content]">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">International Implementations</h3>
        <p>
          From digital democracy projects in Asia (Taiwan) to public
          consultations in Europe (Finland)‚Äîto engage citizens in policymaking
          and foster inclusive, cross-cultural dialogue.
        </p>
        <a href="#">Learn more</a>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup class="h-full grid grid-rows-[3lh_1fr_min-content]">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">North American Experiences</h3>
        <p>
          In the U.S. and Canada, municipalities, universities, and civic groups
          are using Pol.is to tackle local challenges and engage communities in
          shaping their shared future.
        </p>
        <a href="#">Learn more</a>
      </hgroup>
      <hgroup class="h-full grid grid-rows-[3lh_1fr_min-content]">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Local: Toronto Stories</h3>
        <p>
          This section will be updated with outcomes and insights from Public
          Square TO‚Äôs use of Pol.is across Toronto‚Äôs communities as the
          initiative evolves.
        </p>
        <a href="#">Learn more</a>
      </hgroup>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 p-16">
    <h2 class="flex flex-col text-3xl font-bold">
      Upcoming Events
      <span class="font-normal text-base">
        Connect with our volunteers at select events to share feedback on
        policies, projects, and community initiatives using our free platform.
      </span>
    </h2>
  </article>
  <article class="flex flex-col items-center-safe gap-6 text-center p-16">
    <h2 class="flex flex-col max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      Volunteers
      <span class="text-3xl font-bold"> Join Our Team </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-2xl">
      Public Square TO is an initiative brought to life by dedicated volunteers
      from the Civic Tech Toronto community who are passionate about enhancing
      democratic participation in our city.
    </p>
  </article>
</ConvergentLayout>

<style>
  #world-map-container {
    svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: min-content;
    }
  }
</style>
